    "body": "i didn't respond to this particular bit in the previous issue because I didn't think it was the proper place. That said...\n\nWhat exactly is different between what you're suggesting and what we currently have? The prefixes are only used during testing within the cloned GRPC repository to link to the build directory output.\n\nEDIT: and by prefixes, I mean the prefixed CFLAGS etc.\n"
